text:
Hey all, I'm experimenting with the programmable email functionality and I'm running into an issue. I'm trying to show a content block if the price of a deals associated line item is greater than 0. The below works fine:

```{% set x = crm_associations(5304469720, "HubSpot_DEFINED", 19, "", "price", false) %} 
{% if x.results[0].price &gt; 0 %}
  price is greater than 0
{% endif %}```
However, the below does not, I'd like to just loop through associated line items to the deal and include this module in an email being sent from a deal based workflow:

```  {% email_each list="deal.line_items" item="line_item" %}
    {% if line_item.price &gt; 0 %}
      price is greater than 0
    {% endif %}
  {% endemail_each %}```
You'll see a screenshot of the error below, appreciate any insights at all!
